casebody.data:
Michael MISENTI
v.
COMMISSIONER OF CORRECTION. Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided June 21, 2016.

Jeanne M. Zulick, assigned counsel, in support of the petition.

*933Timothy F. Costello, assistant state's attorney, in opposition.

The petitioner Michael Misenti's petition for certification for appeal from the Appellate Court, 165 Conn.App. 548, 140 A.3d 222 (2016), is denied.
